Version 0.3 ():

  New features:
    - new filters to only display upgradable packages and packages
      having pending actions
    - local and remote packages versions are now displayed
    - packages' status now shows the packages which are upgradable


Version 0.2 (2016-02-24):

  New features
    - new '-v' flag added to display version number
    - Page{Up,Down} keys now used to scroll up/down one page

  Bugfixes
    - fix build on i386 


Version 0.1 (2016-02-20):

  - Initial release
